data.name: label11.Text
data.value:
You can easily back up your world by selecting it in the list on the left and clicking 'Generate backup' (the button in bold). If you want to restore a backup, click 'Restore backup' and select the date to which you want to restore to.
You can also import backups from other people. To do that, click 'Import backup' and select the .scrapbackup file. To export backups yourself, click 'Export backup' and save it to a folder, for example your Desktop or your Documents folder.
